Class TokenType

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.adobe.fontengine.font.postscript.TokenType
  • public final class TokenType
extends java.lang.Object
    An enum representing the type of tokens recognized by the Tokenizer class.

    Synchronization

    This class is immutable after contruction and contains no mutable static data. It is therefore threadsafe.
